'''Sequential composition''' of two programs in the context of [[program semantics]] is the [[Composition of relations|relational composition]] of intermediate state:

<math>P_1 ; P_2  \equiv  \exists v_0 \bullet P_1 [ v_0 / v' ]  \land  P_2 [ v_0 / v ]</math>

